  "description": "The DPoP-SK proof-of-possession presentation profile over the JLWS auth surface (cb=none flavour): RFC 9728 pop_session advertisement beside jlws_storage_description, the single dpop_bound_access_tokens_required member covering both PoP profiles, fail-closed client negotiation, session establishment from a DPoP-bound token (and refusal for an unbound one), and per-request RFC 9421 hmac-sha256 attestation with RFC 4303 verify-then-mark anti-replay — accept, tamper, cross-target transplant, token substitution, replay, forged-traffic window integrity, session expiry, and no-bearer-fallback.",
